arts.ttl: SC Paderborn vs. Bayer Leverkusen: DFB-Pokal preview, team news & predicted lineups
arts.sum: Ralf Kettemann’s in-form SC Paderborn welcome Kasper Hjulmand’s Bayer Leverkusen to a sold-out Home Deluxe Arena on Wednesday evening for what promises to be a fascinating second-round DFB-Pokal clash.
